This example requires Mongrel and XmlSimple, if not already installed:

  gem install mongrel
  gem install xml-simple

To run the example, both client and server:

  ruby example.rb

You can also specify the port number like this:

  ruby example.rb 3005

This example will create a new order resource.  The server shows the resource
contents (XML) on the console, the client shows the URL of the new resource.
